<div class="introduction-section">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row">
				
				<div class="col-sm-12">
                <!--<img src="images/we.jpg" alt="" class="pull-right mr_l" width="432" />-->
					<div class="section-title-left">
						Welcome to IAP Group 
						
					</div>
					<div class="introduction-text">
						<p>IAP is an Information, Communication & Technology (ICT) driven business group with interests in the field of</p>
                        <ul>
						<li class="ion-android-add"><a href="#Infotech">Information Technology</a></li>
						<li class="ion-android-add"><a href="#Rollout">Rollout Services</a></li>
						<li class="ion-android-add"><a href="#Media">Media</a></li>
						<li class="ion-android-add"><a href="#eTailing">E-tailing (read- retail + ecommerce)</a></li>
					</ul>
                    <p><strong>INNOVATION</strong>, <strong>ACTION</strong> AND <strong>PERFORMANCE</strong> are the pillars of IAP’s business ETHOS and DNA. These three words together reflect the DNA of IAP.</p>
                    <p>The journey of IAP started two decades ago as a software development company focused on the Japanese IT outsourcing market. Over the years, IAP broadened the business horizon with an aim to build successful businesses at the same time contributing as a responsible organization to build a better society. </p>
                    <a id="Infotech"></a>
                    <p><span class="color01">Infotech :</span> draws its strength from the experience of catering to large customer base in Japan, India and across the globe. Its seasoned team of 1000+ engineers with experience on wide variety of technologies, domains and verticals gives unique technical prowess. </p>
                    <p>IAP Infotech offers wide array of outsourcing services including Software Development, IT Infrastructure Management (IMS), IT Staffing Services in addition to a range of home grown proprietary products & solutions.</p>
                    <div id="Rollout"></div>
                    <p><span class="color01">Rollout Services :</span> is a division of IAP Company Pvt. Ltd. offering unique expertise of implementing, managing and delivering ICT based projects which require last mile / dispersed / distributed / remote / multi-location project management, supervision, whether on field or within office premises. IAP rollout team has successfully implemented various large and mid-sized projects for various government and non-government organizations – including but not limited to enrolments, IT system setup and management, hand holding, capacity building etc.  IAP’s team has project rollout capabilities across the length and breadth of India including the far flung rural areas of every state and union territories. </p>
                    <a id="Media"></a>
                    <p><span class="color01">Media:</span> IAP’s media business is an online venture – <a href="http://www.merinews.com/" target="_blank">www.merinews.com</a>  promoted through the group company Bizsol Advisors Pvt. Ltd. </p>
                    <p>merinews® pioneered the concept of Citizen Journalism in India. Today it stands as the largest and the oldest citizen journalism based news portal in India. It is also featured amongst the top 10 Citizen Powered news platforms of the world. merinews® has various accolades in India and across the world. merinews® is a registered global trade mark of Bizsol Advisors Pvt. Ltd., ( An IAP Group Company). </p>
                    <a id="eTailing"></a>
                    <p><span class="color01">E-tailing :</span> IAP's latest venture merishop™, is a revolutionary concept to take the benefits of Ecommerce and Mobile Internet to the citizens of tier 2,3 cities and rural India. Business of merishop™ finds much credence in the drive for LESS CASH or CASH LESS India as each of the merishop™ is automated, connected on internet, standardized, enabled and promoted cashless transactions with a larger focus to adopt Aadhar Enabled Payment Systems (AEPS) or any other simplified cashless payment mechanism. </p>
                    
                    
					</div>
					
